   Egghead to Have $500,000 Gain
</HL>
<DATE>
04/17/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   EGGS
</CO>
<LP>
   ISSAQUAH, Wash. -- Egghead Discount Software said it will
post a gain of $500,000 from the previously announced sale of
its software training subsidiary to closely held 5750 Inc.
   The unit, known as Egghead University, was founded in 1988
and operates a network of software training centers for
businesses and individuals. Egghead is a high-volume retailer
of personal computer software with about 200 stores
nationwide.
</LP>
